title: Synthesis of sodium (oxalate) difluoro borate-based hybrid electrolyte salts with enhanced interfacial properties for NaNi0.3Fe0.4Mn0.3O2 cathodes
content:
Sustainable Energy Fuels, 2024, Advance Article
DOI: 10.1039/D4SE00118D, Paper
Jia Zhang, Jianwei Li, Guofeng Jia, Huaiyou Wang, Min Wang
In this study, sodium (oxalate) difluoro borate-based hybrid electrolyte salts with enhanced NaNi0.3Fe0.4Mn0.3O2 cathode interface properties were synthesized.
